%F A028177 a(n) = (2*11^(n+3)-3*10^(n+3)+3*6^(n+3)-2*5^(n+3))/60. - _Yahia Kahloune_, Jun 04 2013
%F A028177 a(0)=1, a(1)=32, a(2)=653, a(3)=10864, a(n) = 32*a(n-1)-371*a(n-2)+1840*a(n-3)-3300*a(n-4). - _Harvey P. Dale_, Oct 23 2015
%F A028177 a(n) = 6^(n+1)-5^(n+1)+21*a(n-1)-110*a(n-2). - _Vincenzo Librandi_, Jul 18 2026
%t A028177 CoefficientList[Series[1/((1-5x)(1-6x)(1-10x)(1-11x)),{x,0,20}],x] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Oct 23 2015 *)
